# Project Structure Guide

## üìÅ Recommended Folder Structure

```
ecomart-homepage/
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ public/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ index.html
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ assets/
