## üéØ File Purposes

### Components Directory
Each component is self-contained and reusable:

```
components/Navbar.jsx
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Handles: Navigation, Search, Cart, Profile
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Props: brandName, cartItems, userProfile, handlers
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ State: Search query

components/CategorySection.jsx
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Handles: Category display and navigation
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Props: categories, onCategoryClick, isLoading
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Features: Loading states, click handling

components/FeaturedProducts.jsx
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Handles: Product display and cart actions
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Props: products, onAddToCart, onProductClick
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Features: Discounts, ratings, stock status
```

### Pages Directory
Main page compositions:

```
pages/Homepage.jsx
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Uses: All components
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ State: Local state management
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Data: Default/mock data
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Purpose: Works without backend

pages/HomepageWithBackend.jsx
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Uses: All components + hooks
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ State: API-driven state
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Data: From backend API
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Purpose: Production with backend
```

### Services Directory
API communication layer:

```
services/api.js
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ API_BASE_URL configuration
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Authentication handling
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Request/response processing
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ All API endpoint methods
```

### Hooks Directory
Reusable React hooks:

```
hooks/useApi.js
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ useFetch: Generic data fetching
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ useCategories: Category data
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ useFeaturedProducts: Product data
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ useCart: Cart management
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ useAuth: User authentication
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ useSearch: Search functionality
```

## üîÑ Data Flow

### Standalone Mode (Homepage.jsx)
```
User Action
    ‚Üì
Component Handler (onClick, onChange)
    ‚Üì
Update Local State
    ‚Üì
Re-render Component
    ‚Üì
Display Updated UI
```

### Backend Mode (HomepageWithBackend.jsx)
```
Component Mount
    ‚Üì
Custom Hook (useCategories, useProducts)
    ‚Üì
API Service Call (api.js)
    ‚Üì
Backend API Request
    ‚Üì
Response Processing
    ‚Üì
Update State
    ‚Üì
Re-render with Data

User Action (Add to Cart)
    ‚Üì
Component Handler
    ‚Üì
Custom Hook Method (addToCart)
    ‚Üì
API Service Call
    ‚Üì
Backend Update
    ‚Üì
Refetch Data
    ‚Üì
Update UI
```

## üé® Component Hierarchy

```
App.js
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Homepage (or HomepageWithBackend)
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Navbar
    ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Search Input
    ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Cart Dropdown
    ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Profile Dropdown
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ HeroBanner
    ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ CTA Button
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ CategorySection
    ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Category Cards (map)
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ FeaturedProducts
    ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Product Cards (map)
    ‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Product Image
    ‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Product Details
    ‚îÇ       ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Add to Cart Button
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ServiceStrips
    ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Service Items (map)
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Footer
        ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Brand Info
        ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Category Links
        ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Company Links
        ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Support Links
```

## üì¶ Import Structure

### Component Imports
```javascript
// In Homepage.jsx
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar';
import HeroBanner from '../components/HeroBanner';
import CategorySection from '../components/CategorySection';
import FeaturedProducts from '../components/FeaturedProducts';
import ServiceStrips from '../components/ServiceStrips';
import Footer from '../components/Footer';
```

### Hook Imports
```javascript
// In HomepageWithBackend.jsx
import { 
  useCategories, 
  useFeaturedProducts, 
  useCart, 
  useAuth 
} from '../hooks/useApi';
```

### Service Imports
```javascript
// In hooks/useApi.js
import apiService from '../services/api';
```

## üöÄ Setup Instructions

### Step 1: Create Project Structure
```bash
mkdir -p src/components src/pages src/services src/hooks
```

### Step 2: Copy Files
```bash
# Components
cp Navbar.jsx src/components/
cp HeroBanner.jsx src/components/
cp CategorySection.jsx src/components/
cp FeaturedProducts.jsx src/components/
cp ServiceStrips.jsx src/components/
cp Footer.jsx src/components/

# Pages
cp Homepage.jsx src/pages/
cp HomepageWithBackend.jsx src/pages/

# Services
cp api.js src/services/

# Hooks
cp useApi.js src/hooks/

# Root
cp App.js src/
```

### Step 3: Install Dependencies
```bash
npm install
# or
yarn install
```

### Step 4: Configure Environment
```bash
# Create .env file
echo "REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api" > .env
```

### Step 5: Run Development Server
```bash
npm start
# or
yarn start
```

## üîß Configuration Files

### .env (Environment Variables)
```env
# API Configuration
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api

# Feature Flags (optional)
REACT_APP_ENABLE_SEARCH=true
REACT_APP_ENABLE_CART=true

# Analytics (optional)
REACT_APP_GA_ID=UA-XXXXXXXXX-X
```

### tailwind.config.js (Styling)
```javascript
module.exports = {
  content: [
    "./src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}",
  ],
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  plugins: [require("daisyui")],
  daisyui: {
    themes: ["light", "dark", "cupcake"],
  },
}
```

### package.json (Dependencies)
```json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "react": "^18.2.0",
    "react-dom": "^18.2.0",
    "tailwindcss": "^3.3.0",
    "daisyui": "^4.0.0"
  }
}
```

## üìù File Naming Conventions

### Components
- PascalCase with .jsx extension
- Example: `Navbar.jsx`, `FeaturedProducts.jsx`

### Hooks
- camelCase starting with "use"
- Example: `useApi.js`, `useCart.js`

### Services
- camelCase with .js extension
- Example: `api.js`, `auth.js`

### Pages
- PascalCase with .jsx extension
- Example: `Homepage.jsx`, `CategoryPage.jsx`

## üéØ Import Paths

### Relative Imports
```javascript
// From component to component (same level)
import Navbar from './Navbar';

// From page to component (one level up)
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar';

// From hook to service (one level up)
import apiService from '../services/api';
```

### Absolute Imports (Optional)
Configure in jsconfig.json or tsconfig.json:
```json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "baseUrl": "src"
  }
}
```

Then use:
```javascript
import Navbar from 'components/Navbar';
import { useCart } from 'hooks/useApi';
import apiService from 'services/api';
```

## üîç Quick Reference

### Add New Component
1. Create file in `src/components/NewComponent.jsx`
2. Export as default: `export default NewComponent;`
3. Import in page: `import NewComponent from '../components/NewComponent';`
4. Use in JSX: `<NewComponent />`

### Add New API Endpoint
1. Open `src/services/api.js`
2. Add method to `apiService` object
3. Use in component or create custom hook

### Add New Hook
1. Create file in `src/hooks/useNewHook.js`
2. Import necessary dependencies
3. Export hook function
4. Use in components

### Add New Page
1. Create file in `src/pages/NewPage.jsx`
2. Import required components
3. Compose page layout
4. Add route in App.js (if using routing)

